    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that's a good start. can you go a bit deeper on the 'rule of law' aspect? some of my students feel like they can't quite articulate why prioritizing enforcement is a moral imperative rather than just a logistical one. how would a sophisticated debater frame the ethical necessity of strict enforcement to win over a judge?",
